item.title: About Strynova AI
item.description:
Our Mission

At Strynova AI, we’re on a mission to revolutionize enterprise security through artificial intelligence. Founded in 2019 by a team of cybersecurity experts and AI researchers, we’ve rapidly become a trusted security partner for organizations facing sophisticated cyber threats.
